text: Fred Brock (born November 15, 1974) is a former American football wide receiver. He played for the Arizona Cardinals from 1997 to 1998 and for the New York/New Jersey Hitmen in 2001. ==References== Category:1974 births Category:Living people Category:American football wide receivers Category:Southern Miss Golden Eagles football players Category:Arizona Cardinals players Category:New York/New Jersey Hitmen players
